 redshift z ~ 1 could provide an error on f_NL of the order of a\nfew. This shows the relevance of a joint analysis of galaxy power spectrum and\nbispectrum in future redshift surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2011 20:38:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
