hanism responsible for this\nextraordinary HI tail remains to be determined, our discovery highlights how\nlittle we know about environmental effects in galaxy groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2011 12:44:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
